"Instant buy" and "limit orders" for a bundle of floor NFTs.

This extension will add browsed collections on OpenSea, x2y2, and Looksrare to "limit" or "instant buy" orders. You can choose the number of tokens to buy in a single transaction and save time in critical race for "floor" offers.
